
=== Test Gear client library (libtestgear) ===


1. Introduction

This is the Test Gear client library which offers an API for communicating with
Test Gear device servers. The API allows client applications to connect, load
plugins, query/manage variables, run commands, and finally disconnect from Test
Gear device servers.


2. License

